<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　ぼくは<ruby rubyText="くし">櫛</ruby>の歯みたいな<ruby rubyText="かぎ">鍵</ruby>を作ればいいと考えたこと<sampling type="start" />があるけどね。</sentence>
<sentence>凹のところが０で、凸が１。</sentence>
<sentence>（図７）これを電話機にガシャッと嵌めると、即、通じる。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">森</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　でも、もっといいのは、それを平面的にするわけ。</sentence>
<sentence>一次元でなくて二次元にする。</sentence>
<sentence>そのほうが形で覚えられるでしょ。</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">（図８）</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">安野</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　ああ、そうか。</sentence>
<sentence>中にはすごくカッコいい番号もあるわけだな。</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">市松模様になってたり、真中だけとか…</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">森</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　対角線だけとかね。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">安野</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　四隅とか。</sentence>
<sentence>そんなのは値段が高かったりしてね。</sentence>
<sentence>（笑）これで何本まで表わせるかな。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">森</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　２の十六乗。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">安野</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　ちょっと電卓で計算すると、６５５３６か。</sentence>
<sentence>かなりな数までいける。</sentence>
<sentence>これはいいなあ。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">森</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　この四四・十六で五桁の番号が可能になる。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">安野</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　だから、いっそのこと五五・二十五の桁にすると、相当の数じゃない？</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">森</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　二十五だったらすごいよ。</sentence>
<sentence>３３５５４４３２だから、東京都がいま七桁でしょう。</sentence>
<sentence>これで表わせるね。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">安野</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　まてよ。</sentence>
<sentence>これは天地を決めておかねばいけないぞ。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">森</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　そりゃ、そうです。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">安野</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　それにしても、これは本日の収穫。</sentence>
<sentence>（笑）電電公社に教えてやりたくなったね。</sentence>
<sentence>美しいもの、これは。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
